<br>
Heck even better.. a month ago I was sitting camping my jboots (yes I'm only level 52 and I just tried getting them then).. I just barely managed to kill the spawnholder each time.. and I mean real barely.. using my style.. and living through with like 200-300 hp. When some level 51 magician comes to join me waiting in line hoping to camp jboots for the money. She summons a pet.. sends it in on the next spawnholder and without a pet heal.. nuke or any interference of the magician the earth pet just dartles back to the magician at 34 % of it's health after the fight.<br>
<br>
Did I spend my 1,5 years on this warrior (yes 1,5 years believe it or not.. I've spent half a year camping nagafen for the bloody red scale they felt the need to put a level restriction on).. only to be a bad stat magician pet that can follow complex orders?!<br>
<br>
Really I'm getting tired of how the comparison melee to casters is. A caster is generally in the lower half of the group.. that way more or less being &quot;power leveled&quot; by the melees all their life. Because the melees have to be higher level than the casters to be worth a damn. And if they can't get a group ha who cares.. we're casters we can just quadkite and kill 4 high dark blues no problem.<br>
<br>
And there I sit.. LFG in all the zones across the world and PoP.. hoping for a group.. casting my envy look at the casters.<br>
<br>
And no I'm not asking for warriors to be able to solo here.. but at least give me the feeling I'm worth a damn instead of just a bad magician pet that follows complex orders and hogs up a part of the loot while at it.<br>
<br>
But then again maybe it's just me. I'm getting quite annoyed by it all though. I love being a warrior, but the caster to melee balance in this game is just wrong and with focus items, dot stacking, dot-kiting fix and what not all it's only going worse and worse.<br>
<br>
Good thing we got /shield though! Woopie.. only thing that's good for is for sony to annoy us more with npc's shielding each other.<br>
<br>
And I talk too much I know sue me.. :P Just letting it all out here.. if sony doesn't wake up to reality and gives warriors something decent soon then I'm leaving though I'm sick of it.<br>
<br>
Znort Miasmic<br>
52 warrior<br>
